  "9-28": (
    caption: [Introns and exons. This gene transcript contains five ex- ons and four introns, along with 5(cid:4) and 3(cid:4) untranslated regions (5(cid:4)UTR and 3(cid:4)UTR). Splicing removes the introns to create an mRNA product for translation into protein. c09DNABasedInformationTechnologies.indd Page 344 14/09/12 11:17 AM user-F408 c09DNABasedInformationTechnologies.indd Page 344 14/09/12 11:17 AM user-F408 /Users/user-F408/Desktop /Users/user-F408/Desktop 344 DNA-Based Information Technologies],
